@@ -28,7 +28,7 @@
       },
       {
         "title": "Set up RBAC for Contour",
-        "description": "Ensure that the necessary RBAC permissions are in place for Contour to function correctly.\n```bash\nkubectl apply -f https://projectcontour.io/docs/main/contour-rbac.yaml\n```"
+        "description": "Ensure that the necessary RBAC permissions are in place for Contour to function correctly. RBAC is typically configured automatically by the Helm chart. Verify RBAC is set up:\n```bash\nkubectl get clusterrolebindings | grep contour\n```"
